Package: splitr
Type: Package
Title: Fast Utilities for Splitting Excel Sheets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Daniel", "Amah", email = "danielamahtoday@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a fast function for splitting large Excel sheets into
    multiple smaller sheets using the openxlsx package. The function reads a
    source Excel worksheet, partitions rows into n equal sized chunks, and
    writes each chunk as a styled sheet inside a single workbook. Designed for
    performance when handling large datasets.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    openxlsx,
    data.table
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
